{"tid":1425132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區護照持有人即日起免簽證往伊朗　最長可逗留21日","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:39:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcf9e7efcf169e4e39e26a4785fe51bf4c78f99","tid":1425132,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"特區護照持有人即日起免簽證往伊朗　最長可逗留21日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472102-20190802.htm?fbclid=IwAR0iBh8PFXZw5UUDvvw3Au_XRX7zyozAo1NM7StcRE09u_L1O8x4iKYkE08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472102-20190802.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0iBh8PFXZw5UUDvvw3Au_XRX7zyozAo1NM7StcRE09u_L1O8x4iKYkE08&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=1ca59a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472102-20190802.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0iBh8PFXZw5UUDvvw3Au_XRX7zyozAo1NM7StcRE09u_L1O8x4iKYkE08&h=23df7f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472102-20190802.htm?fbclid=IwAR0iBh8PFXZw5UUDvvw3Au_XRX7zyozAo1NM7StcRE09u_L1O8x4iKYkE08</a><br />\n<br />\n入境處表示，香港特區護照持有人由即日起可免簽證前往伊朗旅遊，最長可逗留21日。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，伊朗是「一帶一路」沿線國家，在「一帶一路」倡議下，免簽證安排會為香港遊客帶來更大便利，有助加強兩地在旅遊、文化和經濟方面的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n連同伊朗在內，已有共166個國家或地區給予香港特區護照持有人免簽證或落地簽證待遇。"},{"pid":"471811c700e59d39c9250378e799645f521069da","tid":1425132,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:39:13.000Z","msg":"得鬼閒去呢D垃圾鬼國,伊朗繼續死去幫中共上前線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}